	   <tr><td colspan=2>Leather should not be hard to find.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you cant find it at a merchant, then you can contact a tailor and they can make you one from a medium quality wolf hide and a pattern.  very cheap that way if you go kill the wolf your self.  LQ pelts make patchwork. and MQ pelts make leather, i believe.  But you could settle for patchwork because I believe it looks the same as leather.<br><br>good luck.<br>&nbsp;<br>Be Safe in the Shadows:-)<br><br>~Ivan~<br></td></tr>
