	   <tr><td colspan=2>Patience and a lot of practice.&nbsp;&nbsp;You should have duel wield now so I would recommend have your best damage piercer in the primary and Pick the lowest delay with decent damage 1hs for you secondary.  This way you raise your duel wield and 1hs at the same time.  I will take at least 5 levels before your 1hs skill would catch up.<br><br>You could also just use two piercers at once when you try to solo but grouping situations would be the best opportunity to put the 1hs in the primary.<br><br>Good luck<br>&nbsp;<br>Be Safe in the Shadows:-)<br><br>~Ivan~<br></td></tr>
