	   <tr><td colspan=2>Bah, don't drop the str at all.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you can increase the agl then fine but you get less bang for you buck that way.  Str totally helps you hit for more damage and with backstabs, it makes a big difference.  Plus, it allows the rogue to stay out in the wild much longer without having to make runs to town.  AGL is nice but if you are grouping like a rogue should be doing at your level, you are not going to be getting hit as much because you can evade combat and backstab while the traditional Tanks absorb the damage.<br>&nbsp;<br>Be Safe in the Shadows:-)<br><br>~Ivan~<br></td></tr>
